        break
    except:
        page+=1

from functools import reduce
import re
amountList=[]

for string in nameList:
    p=re.compile("\d+(ml|ML)(.*\d+[팩개입])*",re.S)
    m=p.search(string)
    try:
        result=m.group()
        amounts=re.findall("\d+",result)
        amount=int(reduce(lambda x,y:int(x)*int(y),amounts))
    except:
        amount=np.nan
        
    amountList.append(amount)
    
print(amountList)

def remove_comma(string):
    num=int(re.sub("(\d+),(\d+)",r"\1\2",string))
    return num

priceList=list(map(remove_comma,priceList))

from selenium import webdriver

chromedriver_path = 'C:/Users/miny0/CSP_python/chromedriver'
driver = webdriver.Chrome(chromedriver_path) 
page=1

nameList=[]
priceList=[]
while True:
    url =f"http://browse.gmarket.co.kr/search?keyword=%ec%9a%94%ea%b5%ac%eb%a5%b4%ed%8a%b8&k=27&p={page}"
    driver.get(url)
    names=driver.find_elements_by_css_selector("span.text__item")
    prices=driver.find_elements_by_css_selector("strong.text.text__value")
    for name,price in zip(names,prices):
        nameList.append(name.text)
        priceList.append(price.text)
    
    try:
        driver.find_element_by_css_selector("span[title='마지막 페이지 입니다']")
        break
    except:
        page+=1
        
print(len(priceList))
print(priceList)

#요구르트
from selenium import webdriver
from functools import reduce
import re
import numpy as np
amountList=[]

for string in nameList:
    p=re.compile("\d+(ml|ML)(.*\d+[팩개입])*",re.S)
    m=p.search(string)
    try:
        result=m.group()
        amounts=re.findall("\d+",result)
        amount=int(reduce(lambda x,y:int(x)*int(y),amounts))
        if amount==0:
            amount=np.nan
    except:
        amount=np.nan
        
    amountList.append(amount)
    
print(amountList)

from selenium import webdriver

chromedriver_path = 'C:/Users/miny0/CSP_python/chromedriver'
driver = webdriver.Chrome(chromedriver_path) 
page=1

nameList=[]
priceList=[]
while True:
    url =f"http://browse.gmarket.co.kr/search?keyword=%eb%93%b1%ec%8b%ac&k=26&p={page}"
    driver.get(url)
    names=driver.find_elements_by_css_selector("span.text__item")
    prices=driver.find_elements_by_css_selector("strong.text.text__value")
    for name,price in zip(names,prices):
        nameList.append(name.text)
        priceList.append(price.text)
    
    try:
        driver.find_element_by_css_selector("span[title='마지막 페이지 입니다']")
        break
    except:
        page+=1
        
print(len(priceList))
print(priceList)

from selenium import webdriver
from functools import reduce
import re
import numpy as np
amountList=[]

for string in nameList:
    p=re.compile("\d+(g)(.*\d+[팩개입])*",re.S)
    m=p.search(string)
    try:
        result=m.group()
        amounts=re.findall("\d+",result)
        amount=int(reduce(lambda x,y:int(x)*int(y),amounts))
        if amount==0:
            amount=np.nan
    except:
        amount=np.nan
        
    amountList.append(amount)
    
print(amountList)

def remove_comma(string):

        num=int(re.sub("(\d+),(\d+)",r"\1\2",string))
    except:
        num=int(re.sub("(\d+),(\d+),(\d+)",r"\1\2\3",string))
    return num

priceList=list(map(remove_comma,priceList))
priceList

from selenium import webdriver

chromedriver_path = 'C:/Users/miny0/CSP_python/chromedriver'
driver = webdriver.Chrome(chromedriver_path) 
page=1

nameList=[]
priceList=[]
while True:
    url =f"http://browse.gmarket.co.kr/search?keyword=%ea%b3%a0%eb%93%b1%ec%96%b4&k=26&p={page}"
    driver.get(url)
    names=driver.find_elements_by_css_selector("span.text__item")
    prices=driver.find_elements_by_css_selector("strong.text.text__value")
    for name,price in zip(names,prices):
        nameList.append(name.text)
        priceList.append(price.text)
    
    try:
        driver.find_element_by_css_selector("span[title='마지막 페이지 입니다']")
        break
    except:
        page+=1
        
print(len(priceList))
print(priceList)

result=np.array([])
for i in range(len(df1)):
    if df1['unit_str'].iloc[i]=="(1KG당)":
        result=np.append(result,df1['avg'].iloc[i]/1000)
    else:
        result=np.append(result,df1['avg'].iloc[i])

result1=[]
for i in range(len(foodKinds_product)):
    foodType=foodKinds_product[i]
    total_cost=0
    for food,amount in zip(foodType,list(current_per.values())):
        cost=foodCost.loc[food,"cost_per"]
        total_cost+=cost*amount
    result1.append(total_cost)
